  <brief_title>Rituximab Desensitization Therapy for Patients on the Waiting List for Kidney Transplant</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter Trial Using Multi-dose Rituximab as Induction and Desensitization Therapy for Patients on the Waiting List for Kidney Transplant With a Positive Donor Specific Crossmatch to a Living Donor</official_title>
